## Embeddings Support

Generate embeddings for extracted text using the built-in ONNX Runtime support:

```python
from kreuzberg import Extractor, EmbeddingsConfig

config = EmbeddingsConfig(
    enabled=True,
    model_name="all-MiniLM-L6-v2"
)

extractor = Extractor(config)
result = extractor.extract("document.pdf")
embeddings = result.embeddings
```

Requires ONNX Runtime installation - see [Embeddings Guide](https://kreuzberg.dev/features/#embeddings).

